                    Prime Minister Attlee to President Truman</title></titleStmt><sourceDesc><bibl type="frus-volume-id">frus1945Berlinv02</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-id">d1314</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-number">1314</bibl><bibl type="frus-div-subtype">historical-document</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><settingDesc><setting><date notBefore="1945-08-01T00:00:00-05:00" notAfter="1945-08-01T23:59:59-05:00"/></setting></settingDesc>            <textClass>
